channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: RNC Speakers Are Being Announced, but Here's Who Has Not Gotten an Invite - and It Is a Bad Idea
Senate Dems to test whether abortion can break through talk of Biden concerns
item.description: Democrats will try to cut through discussion of President Biden's status as the Democratic candidate for president in November on Wednesday with a vote to put Republicans on record as it relates to abortion.

item.title: Vulnerable Dem Rep. Pat Ryan Calls on Biden to Drop Out
item.description: Rep. Pat Ryan, a New York Democrat running for reelection in a competitive district, in an interview on Wednesday called on President Joe Biden to drop out of the 2024 presidential election "for the good of the country."

item.title: Harvard Caves, Retracts Suspensions for Five Pro-Hamas Protestors
Democrats say calls to replace Biden after primaries aren't 'threat to democracy,' a charge lobbed at Trump
item.description: Democrats in the Senate were reluctant to claim calls from elites and celebrities to replace President Biden on the Democratic ticket were a "threat to democracy."

item.title: Ocasio-Cortez Seeks Impeachment of Supreme Court's Thomas, Alito
item.description: Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez a liberal New York Democrat, has introduced articles of impeachment against conservative U.S. Supreme Court Justices Clarence Thomas and Samuel Alito, her office said Wednesday.The effort stands no chance of advancing in the...

item.title: Biden Botches Quote at NATO Summit, What He Says Instead Is a Revelatory Freudian Slip
Veepstakes: Trump handicaps three of his top running mate contenders
item.description: Former President Trump, in a Fox News interview, handicaps Doug Burgum, JD Vance, and Marco Rubio, three top contenders for Republican running mate

item.title: Increasingly Defiant Biden Borrows Tactics From Trump
item.description: Longtime watchers of President Donald Trump say there is something familiar in some of the ways President Joe Biden has pushed back at criticism.

item.title: Director of National Intelligence: Iran's 'Foreign Actors' Stoking Trouble in America
AOC files articles of impeachment against Justices Alito, Thomas, alleges 'unchecked corruption'
item.description: Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez filed articles of impeachment against Supreme Court Justices Samuel Alito and Clarence Thomas on Wednesday.

item.title: Washington: Crime Victims Should Worry About REPAIR Act
item.description: Imagine a woman who has just escaped an abusive boyfriend or husband. She grabbed her kids and drove off in her car. If this bill passes, her abuser could track her every move. Those bent on power and control will use every tool they can.

item.title: Biden Reveals What 'They' Warned Him Not to Do at AFL-CIO Event, Then Reporters Are Tossed, Feed Cuts Out
Biden advisers to join Senate Dems for special meeting amid swelling concerns
item.description: The Biden campaign is sending several top advisers to a special meeting of Senate Democrats as the lawmakers reveal their concerns about his condition.

item.title: Rep. Harris to Newsmax: Public Sees Right Through WH Deception on Biden
item.description: The public knows that the White House is not telling the truth about President Joe Biden's mental condition, Rep. Andy Harris told Newsmax on Wednesday.
